game.function.game.line234: The first ever official Rogues 2 tournament! Many more to come <3
game.function.game.line254:
While souls cross over, they pass just by the world of dead. Mischievous spirits play with these lost souls, grabbing them up and returning them to the spirit realm.

In legend, the life lived by a soul can be understood by which spirit is chosen to return it.

As they vigorously fight, sometimes souls touch the spirits many times. Eventually, however, every soul is returned, when the world finally decides what spirit should be the guild.

game.function.players.charactersel.line9:
_____________________________________________________

Souls taken by Â§cSparketÂ§f were of truly free-spirited people.

If a person keeps themselves and their family free, Sparket will bring warmth to their home. If a person is so obsessed with freedom as to become careless, Sparket will roar their fire and burn them down.
game.function.players.charactersel.line1:
_____________________________________________________

Souls taken by Â§bEmmaÂ§f were people who belonged to the sea.

All sailors owe their soul to the sea. When a man refuses his call to the sea, great rains will come and flood his town.
game.function.players.charactersel.line2:
_____________________________________________________

People with souls of a spider are taken by Â§6HaltÂ§f.

Spiders are cruel to all. However, spider souls are close to the spirit world. People with a spider soul often become oracles and give divine orders.

The word of a spider soul must be followed. Those who disobey will be bit by spiders while they sleep.

_____________________________________________________

Souls taken by Â§7PlutoÂ§f are of corrupt people.

Those who practice corrupt magic should be outcast by their clan. Their souls are tainted.

Pluto is a forgiving spirit. He is the only spirit that will guide these souls, after they grow too tired to haunt the earth.

If a person is outcast unjustly, Pluto will protect them in life.
game.function.players.charactersel.line3:
_____________________________________________________

Souls taken by Â§eBarboseÂ§f are from fearful, weak people.

When a person becomes fearful of death, Barbose comes and steals their warmth. If a person becomes obsessed with avoiding death, Barbose leads them to it.

_____________________________________________________

Souls taken by Â§aVohelmÂ§f are from warriors. To be guided by Vohelm is a great honor.

The human world is a dangerous one, and Vohelm protects those who protect their family. Abandon your family, and he abandons you.

Many families build statues to honor Vohelm and bring him into their home.
